{"tid":2070900,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求救政府開始追稅 - 1蚊交稅大法","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T14:19:09.000Z","uid":40072,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c38edc1de67303d6a424d3450d25a63dd1eefb","tid":2070900,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，細佬我發夢由今年年頭收到稅單開始實行1蚊交稅大法（用恒生信用卡每日狂㩒範本，每日交50蚊），預計要交到下年都未交完，已經過期幾個月，今日收到稅局追稅信（如下圖），咁如果細佬我繼續1蚊咁交唔理佢封信會點？有冇人知？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7y7GVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7y7GVQ.jpg&h=04c43f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人仲好似我咁堅持緊1蚊交稅或者索性唔交？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好憎交稅俾政府倒落海，最憎交稅俾政府請黑警打香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc9ab0226d20c8dbaf0639678d31a682691034","tid":2070900,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"遲交咪罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903303ca9a93c6cf6eb7eee8f10e8bdd43f5e6e1","tid":2070900,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"黃的APPS 「巴絲GO」關於審核司機問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2069741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2069741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a635fad3f3bac89566f4afe6a8978f92e39981ac","tid":2070900,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"佢會要你公司凍結出糧畀你"},{"pid":"1018f03e32e44e7509185883d7b13cc7b4d28aa1","tid":2070900,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a635fad3f3bac89566f4afe6a8978f92e39981ac","tid":2070900,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"佢會要你公司凍結出糧畀你"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"咁大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb1e28067aa5c8b8ea01e244f83c28ad33d653d"